      "rationale": "Validation was performed on the same FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry as the COU device. Fluid (bovine blood, viscosity matched to human blood at 37 °C), operating range, and boundary conditions are representative. Minor geometric differences between the test article and the nominal COU geometry are within manufacturing tolerances and documented."
    },
    {
