      "acceptanceCriteria": "Turbulence model and hemolysis damage model selection must be justified with reference to published validation evidence for rotating blood-contacting devices.",
      "rationale": "The SST k-omega turbulence model was selected based on published literature demonstrating superior performance in rotating machinery flows with adverse pressure gradients. The Giersiepen-Wurzinger power-law hemolysis model was adopted consistent with FDA guidance and prior centrifugal pump validation studies. Model form choices are documented and justified."
